<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <title>RCVD - Announcement</title>
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .announcement ul {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .announcement ul li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .announcement ul li::before {
      content: "âœ…";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: green;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <div class="container announcement">
    <main>
      <section>
        <h2>Announcement</h2>
        <p>
          RCVD is a regulatory body mandated to regulate the veterinary profession. Its general mission is to ensure that its members (veterinary professionals and para-professionals) provide quality and reliable services in the following areas:
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>Curative and preventive veterinary medicine</li>
          <li>Animal reproduction</li>
          <li>Veterinary pharmacy practice and use of inputs and livestock equipment</li>
          <li>Hygiene and quality of animal products</li>
          <li>Wild animal medicine</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
